# Input

```yml
- # Empty
- |
 block node
- - one # Compact
  - two # sequence
- one: two # Compact mapping

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1,4 +1,4 @@
--  # Empty
+- # Empty
 - |
   block node
 - - one # Compact
```

# Output

```yml
- # Empty
- |
  block node
- - one # Compact
  - two # sequence
- one: two # Compact mapping
```
